seller.description: Hello and welcome to my profile! I'm Nouman, and I'm delighted that you stopped by. With a track record of more than 4000 5-star reviews, I've successfully wrapped up 6500 projects spanning across 100+ countries. For over a decade, I've been honing my expertise in email hosting configuration, domain authentication, and email migration. Looking forward to bringing my experience to work for you!

reviews.comment: DO NOT TRY TO SET UP SPF, DMARC, DKIM ON YOUR OWN! Hire Nouman! Seriously, if you don't have the experience you will waste so much time by being cheap trying to figure out how to do it yourself. I did because I wasn't comfortable giving out my log in info, but then we passed the deadline to be compliant with Google and my customers weren't getting my emails. Not good! I'm happy I hired Nouman. Turn around was quick and he answered all of my questions. He is also very affordable.

We needed our DMARC Google authentication set up and after reading several 5 star reviews of Nouman's work - and specifically for the exact same DMARC projects - we went ahead and are very happy with the work completed. He stepped me through several tasks I needed to complete in order for him to action the project. Our Klaviyo, Google Account and Shopify platforms have all been set up and/or connected and the project was completed in a matter of days. I highly recommend engaging Nouman as very professional, responsive online and swift turnaround on completing our project. Thank you!

Nouman was great to work with for this project. With the Google/Yahoo deadline looming, I was trying to figure out my SPF, DKIM, and DMARC configuration to no avail. After seeing Nouman's 5 star rating and reading a few reviews, I figured it was better to trust an expert. He was quick to respond, answered all of my questions and took care of all the configurations I needed to stay compliant. Nouman definitely earns his 5 stars! Thank you.

Within a short time of ordering, and despite my reluctance to submit log-in details through Fiverr, Nouman completed the work through an easy work-around to the log-in issue (using Zoom).
He made sure to check along with me that all my domain records are set correctly and that emails pass the test successfully.
Highly recommend, I will surely use Nouman's services again when needed!

the DMARC situation is something I worried over for weeks before finally deciding to seek pro help. If you're reading this just stop now and let Nouman handle your worries for you! He is wonderful, professional, patient and kind and will do an amazing job for you! Thank you Nouman!
